  "description": "This morning, I\u0026rsquo;m planning on adding Org-cite to GnoponEmacs.\nI\u0026rsquo;m reading a series of guides on Org-cite, starting with the announcement post from the Org-mode mailing list, and looking at how it distinguishes between citation interaction and rendering, the role of citation processors (basic, biblatex, natbib, csl), and how to hook this into my own bibliography orgcite.bib.\nI\u0026rsquo;ve added an example BibTeX entry for Jens Kipper\u0026rsquo;s A Two-Dimensionalist Guide to Conceptual Analysis and verified that [@Kipper2012] and #+print_bibliography: work in exported text.\n",
  "name": "2025-08-28, 0853h, Adding org-cite to gnoponemacs",
